text: City West is an area in the centre of Berlin, Germany. City West or similar terms may also refer to: * City West, Indiana, USA, an abandoned village * Citywest, Dublin, Ireland, a business park and suburb * City West Housing Trust, Salford, Greater Manchester, England, a housing association * CityWest Homes, a housing association in Westminster, London * City West railway station, Perth, Australia * CityWest, a cable company and ISP in British Columbia, Canada
title: City West (disambiguation)
